name: Saudade
description: I took this photo in 2018, with the first humble and cheap camera I could offer at that time. After 6 months I took this photo, I had to move away from my family and homeland due to money problems. "Saudade" in Portuguese is the word for missing something, someone, somewhere. Has been 3 years since I saw my grandparents and my childhood friends, and I miss them from the bottom of my heart.
